# Purpose

Enforce frontend folder structure, dependency direction, and layer boundaries.

# Rules

## Folder Structure

```
frontend/src/
├── _types/         Generated API types (_gen) and infrastructure interfaces
├── api/            HTTP client + per-resource service functions
│   └── service/
│       ├── client/ (rest.ts, stream.ts)
│       └── resources/<resource>/
├── components/
│   ├── ui/         shadcn/ui primitives (auto-generated, DO NOT edit manually)
│   ├── ui-app/     App-level wrapper components (Button, Field, Text, etc.)
│   ├── layout/     Layout components (Sidebar, TopBar, Dashboard, Authenticate)
│   ├── container/  Container-level page wrappers
│   └── pages/      Page components per route
├── hooks/          Custom React hooks
├── services/       Browser services (error, logging, storage)
├── shared/         Shared schemas and types
├── store/          Zustand store (slices + selectors)
└── utils/          Pure utility functions
```

## Dependency Direction

`pages/` → `ui-app/`, `api/`, `store/`, `services/`, `utils/`, `shared/`  
`ui-app/` → `ui/` (shadcn primitives only)  
`store/` → state shape only, no API calls  
`api/` → `services/error`, `store` (for access token) only

# Anti-Patterns

- DO NOT add API calls inside Zustand store slices.
- DO NOT import from `components/ui/` directly in pages or features — use `ui-app/` wrappers.
- DO NOT manually edit files in `src/components/ui/` — managed exclusively by the shadcn CLI (`npm run scadd`).
- DO NOT manually edit files in `src/_types/_gen/` — generated by Orval (`npm run generate-types`).
